github profile link is a phpBB 3.0 modification which adds a new profile field for github. It it displayed on viewtopic, viewprofile, ucp_pm_viewmessage, ucp, acp.

INSTALL

See install.xml for installation instructions. You can also find help at phpBB.com <http://www.phpbb.com/mods/> or use the installation tool <http://www.phpbb.com/mods/automod/>.

This modification uses UMIL <http://www.phpbb.com/mods/umil/>. If you are using the development version, you need to add UMIL manually. The version used can be found in develop/UMIL_VERSION.

